'''伊莉莎白·安妮·霍姆斯'''（Elizabeth Anne Holmes；{{bd|1984年|2月3日||}}），血液检测公司[[Theranos|Theranos]]的创始人<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/04/25/business/theranoss-fate-rests-with-afounder-who-answers-only-to-herself.html?_r=1 | title=Theranos’s Fate Rests With a Founder Who Answers Only to Herself | publisher=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]] | date=2016-04-24 | accessdate=2016-04-30 | author=Abelson, Reed | archive-date=2020-11-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108133127/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/04/25/business/theranoss-fate-rests-with-afounder-who-answers-only-to-herself.html?_r=1 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，此公司位于美國[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]的[[帕罗奥多|帕罗奥多]]，一度是[[生物科技|生物科技]]行業的[[独角兽_(公司)|獨角獸公司]]，因為聲稱提出創新的，只需少量血液即可進行的[[血液检查|血液检查]]而聞名，已經解散<ref>{{cite news|last1=Levine|first1=Matt|title=The Blood Unicorn Theranos Was Just a Fairy Tale|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/view/articles/2018-03-14/theranos-misled-investors-and-consumers-who-used-its-blood-test|accessdate=2018-03-14|work=Bloomberg View|date=2018-03-14|archive-date=2018-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180314200115/https://www.bloomberg.com/view/articles/2018-03-14/theranos-misled-investors-and-consumers-who-used-its-blood-test|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/04/25/business/theranoss-fate-rests-with-afounder-who-answers-only-to-herself.html?_r=1 | title=Theranos’s Fate Rests With a Founder Who Answers Only to Herself | newspaper=New York Times | date=2016-04-24 | accessdate=2016-04-30 | author=Abelson, Reed | archive-date=2018-06-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613004650/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/04/25/business/theranoss-fate-rests-with-afounder-who-answers-only-to-herself.html?_r=1 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180905004716-260410 |title=血液檢測公司Theranos 矽谷最大詐騙公司解散 |author=吳慧珍 |date=2018-09-05 |work=中國時報 |accessdate=2018-09-22 |archive-date=2020-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200613060122/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180905004716-260410 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年時，《[[富比士|富比士]]》因為公司估值90亿美元，将霍姆斯评选为全球最年轻、白手起家的女性亿万富翁<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/self-made-women/list/|title=America's Richest Self-Made Women|publisher=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|access-date=2016-11-05|archive-date=2020-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010222555/https://www.forbes.com/self-made-women/list/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，她也曾被《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》提名为「2015年前100名最有影响力人物」<ref name="time-april-2015">{{cite web | url=http://time.com/3822734/elizabeth-holmes-2015-time-100/ | title=The 100 Most Influential People: Elizabeth Holmes | publisher=TIME | date=2015-04-16 | accessdate=2016-06-11 | author=Kissinger, Henry A. | archive-date=2016-06-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160605210115/http://time.com/3822734/elizabeth-holmes-2015-time-100/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。次年富比士将她的资产估值「从45亿美元更新为一文不值」<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites#/sites/matthewherper/2016/06/01/from-4-5-billion-to-nothing-forbes-revises-estimated-net-worth-of-theranos-founder-elizabeth-holmes/#90e84982f29a|title=From $4.5 Billion To Nothing: Forbes Revises Estimated Net Worth Of Theranos Founder Elizabeth Holmes|last=Herper|first=Matthew|date=2016-06-01|publisher=Forbes|access-date=2017-01-06|archive-date=2017-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170307204934/https://www.forbes.com/sites/#/sites/matthewherper/2016/06/01/from-4-5-billion-to-nothing-forbes-revises-estimated-net-worth-of-theranos-founder-elizabeth-holmes/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而《[[财富杂志|财富杂志]]》将霍姆斯称作为“世上最让人失望的领导者”<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://fortune.com/2016/03/30/most-disappointing-leaders/|title=The World's 19 Most Disappointing Leaders|date=2016-03-30|website=Fortune|access-date=2016-12-02|archive-date=2016-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161123145216/http://fortune.com/2016/03/30/most-disappointing-leaders/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年起，新闻媒體和监管机构開始質疑Theranos宣称内容的真实性，並且懷疑霍姆斯有意誤導投資者以及政府有關其驗血技術的資訊，此時Theranos就開始走下坡。2018年時[[美国证券交易委员会|美国证券交易委员会]]對Theranos和霍姆斯利用誇大或虛假的聲稱欺騙消費者，進行「大規模詐騙」提出訴訟，後來霍姆斯為此事付了五十萬美金的罰金、交還其股份、放棄對Theranos的投票控制權、並且十年內禁止擔任上市公司的高級職員或董事。2018年6月時{{le|聯邦大陪審團|federal grand jury}}起訴霍姆斯及Theranos前營運長{{le|Ramesh Balwani|Ramesh Balwani}}九項電匯詐騙罪以及二項串謀電匯詐騙罪<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|author=Johnson, Carolyn Y.|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/business/economy/elizabeth-holmes-founder-of-blood-testing-company-theranos-indicted-on-wire-fraud-federal-authorities-announce/2018/06/15/8779f538-70df-11e8-bd50-b80389a4e569_story.html|title=Elizabeth Holmes, founder of blood-testing company Theranos, indicted on wire fraud charges|work=Washington Post|date=2018-06-15|language=en-US|issn=0190-8286|accessdate=2018-09-22|archive-date=2019-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191011102418/https://www.washingtonpost.com/business/economy/elizabeth-holmes-founder-of-blood-testing-company-theranos-indicted-on-wire-fraud-federal-authorities-announce/2018/06/15/8779f538-70df-11e8-bd50-b80389a4e569_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="StepsDown">[https://www.reuters.com/article/theranos-ceo/theranos-founder-elizabeth-holmes-steps-down-as-ceo-idUSL4N1TH5TY Theranos founder Elizabeth Holmes steps down as CEO] {{Wayback|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/theranos-ceo/theranos-founder-elizabeth-holmes-steps-down-as-ceo-idUSL4N1TH5TY |date=20190626212741 }}, Reuters (2018-06-15).</ref>。

霍姆斯個人認識許多有影響力的人士，並且受到其支持，這些人包括美國前国务卿[[亨利·基辛格|亨利·基辛格]]、前国务卿[[乔治·普拉特·舒尔茨|乔治·普拉特·舒尔茨]]、前國防部長[[詹姆斯·马蒂斯|詹姆斯·马蒂斯]]、教育部長[[贝琪·德沃斯|贝琪·德沃斯]]及前国务卿[[希拉里·克林顿|希拉里·克林顿]]。<!--霍姆斯曾和Theranos的營運長Ramesh Balwani，當時兩人分別是18歲及37歲。-->霍姆斯已成為《[[惡血：矽谷獨角獸的醫療騙局！深藏血液裡的祕密、謊言與金錢|惡血：矽谷獨角獸的醫療騙局！深藏血液裡的祕密、謊言與金錢]]》及將上映同名電影的主要人物。

==早年生活==
霍姆斯出生於[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿哥伦比亚特区]]<ref name="nytTest">{{cite web | url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/12/20/business/theranos-founder-faces-a-test-of-technology-and-reputation.html?_r=0 | title=Theranos Founder Faces a Test of Technology, and Reputation | work=New York Times | date=2015-12-19 | accessdate=2016-12-01 | author1=Abelson, Reed | author2=Creswe, Julie | archive-date=2017-01-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170120161553/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/12/20/business/theranos-founder-faces-a-test-of-technology-and-reputation.html?_r=0 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，她的父親克里斯丁·拉斯穆斯·福爾摩斯四世（Christian Rasmus Holmes IV）曾經擔任[[安隆公司|-{zh-cn:安然公司; zh-hk:安然公司; zh-tw:安隆公司;}-]]的副總裁，之後在[[美国国际开发署|美国国际开发署]]、[[美国国家环境保护局|美国国家环境保护局]]及{{link-en|美國貿易署|United States Trade and Development Agency}}擔任行政職位<ref name="ChristianHolmesBloomberg">{{cite web|title=Company Overview of Ze-gen Inc: Executive Profile: Christian Holmes|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/person.asp?personId=58650162&privcapId=28826738|accessdate=2018-09-04|publisher=Bloomberg|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327100027/https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/person.asp?personId=58650162&privcapId=28826738|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ChristianHolmesBio">{{cite web|title=Christian Holmes|url=https://www.bcg.com/en-us/about/people/experts/christian-holmes.aspx|accessdate=2018-09-04|publisher=The Boston Consulting Group|archive-date=2018-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180905141103/https://www.bcg.com/en-us/about/people/experts/christian-holmes.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="auto">{{cite news |url=https://www.wired.com/2014/02/elizabeth-holmes-theranos/?cid=18964974 |title=This Woman Invented a Way to Run 30 Lab Tests on Only One Drop of Blood |first=Caitlin |last=Roper |date=2014-02-18 |work=Wired |accessdate=2018-09-27 |archive-date=2015-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151219223457/http://www.wired.com/2014/02/elizabeth-holmes-theranos/?cid=18964974 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name = "Bilton">Bilton, N. [http://www.vanityfair.com/news/2016/09/elizabeth-holmes-theranos-exclusive "Exclusive: How Elizabeth Holmes's House of Cards Came Tumbling Down"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/news/2016/09/elizabeth-holmes-theranos-exclusive |date=20170410172642 }}. ''Vanity Fair'', October 2016, retrieved December 5, 2016.</ref>。霍姆斯的母親諾埃爾·安妮·道斯特（Noel Anne Daoust）是[[美国国会职员|美国国会职员]]<ref name="newy_OneW">{{Cite web | title = One Woman’s Drive to Revolutionize Medical Testing | author = Auletta, Ken | work = The New Yorker | date = 2014-12-15 | accessdate = 2015-10-19 | url = http://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2014/12/15/blood-simpler | archive-date = 2019-10-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191028084933/https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2014/12/15/blood-simpler | dead-url = no }}</ref>。她的曾祖父克里斯丁·拉斯穆斯·福爾摩斯（Christian Rasmus Holmes）是丹麥裔的醫生，和富家千金贝蒂·弗莱施曼（Bettie Fleischmann）結婚，贝蒂的父親是{{link-en|Fleischmann's Yeast|Fleischmann's Yeast}}的創辦人{{link-en|查理·路易斯·弗萊施曼|Charles Louis Fleischmann}}<ref name="New York Times">{{Cite web | title = Theranos Founder Faces a Test of Technology, and Reputation | author = Abelson, Reed and Julie Creswell | work = The New York Times | date = 2015-12-19 | accessdate = 2018-07-10 | url = https://mobile.nytimes.com/2015/12/20/business/theranos-founder-faces-a-test-of-technology-and-reputation.html | archive-date = 2018-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180711021906/https://mobile.nytimes.com/2015/12/20/business/theranos-founder-faces-a-test-of-technology-and-reputation.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

霍姆斯就讀休斯頓的{{le|聖約翰學校 (德州)|St. John's School (Texas)|聖約翰學校}}<ref name="nytTest"/>，在高中時對[[電腦程式|電腦程式]]有興趣<ref name="Roger2014">{{cite news |url=http://fortune.com/2014/06/12/theranos-blood-holmes/ |title=This CEO is out for blood |work=[[Fortune_(magazine)|Fortune]] |first=Roger |last=Parloff |date=2014-06-12 |accessdate=2018-09-27 |archive-date=2019-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191007102223/https://fortune.com/2014/06/12/theranos-blood-holmes/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。霍姆斯在2001年申請史丹佛大學，就讀化工系，在實驗室中和數位博士研究生以及工程学院院长[[錢寧·羅伯遜|錢寧·羅伯遜]]（Channing Robertson）一起工作<ref name="newy_OneW"/>。

霍姆斯在一年級下學期進入{{le|新加坡基因組研究中心|Genome Institute of Singapore}}的實驗室工作，在針筒搜集的血液樣本中檢驗[[嚴重急性呼吸系統綜合症|嚴重急性呼吸系統綜合症]]（SARS）<ref name="Roger2014" />，她在2003年申請第一個專利，內容是可穿戴的給药贴片<ref name="inc-oct-2015">{{cite web|author=Weisul, Kimberly|url=http://www.inc.com/magazine/201510/kimberly-weisul/the-longest-game.html|title=How Playing the Long Game Made Elizabeth Holmes a Billionaire|work=Inc.com|accessdate=2016-04-08|archive-date=2019-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191214004145/https://www.inc.com/magazine/201510/kimberly-weisul/the-longest-game.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="inc-july-2015">{{Cite web|url=http://www.inc.com/larry-kim/21-surprising-facts-about-the-world-s-youngest-female-billionaire.html|title=21 Surprising Facts About Billionaire Entrepreneur Elizabeth Holmes|work=Inc.|author=Kim, Larry|date=2015-07-01|access-date=2016-10-17|archive-date=2016-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160727221353/http://www.inc.com/larry-kim/21-surprising-facts-about-the-world-s-youngest-female-billionaire.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。霍姆斯在2004年3月時離開史丹佛大學工學院，將她的學費作為消费性医疗保健技术公司的種子基金<ref name ="CNNMoney" /><ref name="newy_OneW"/>。

==Theranos公司==
<!--{{Main|Theranos}}-->

===成立===
霍姆斯在加州的帕羅奧圖成立了Real-Time Cures公司，宗旨是「醫療保健的民主化」<ref name="auto"/><ref name="Roger2014" /><ref name="Roger2014"/><ref name="NYT-oct-2015">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2015/10/12/t-magazine/elizabeth-holmes-tech-visionaries-brian-chesky.html?_r=1|title=Five Visionary Tech Entrepreneurs Who Are Changing the World: Elizabeth Holmes|work=The New York Times|author=Arrillaga-Andreessen, Laura|date=2015-10-12|access-date=2016-08-11|archive-date=2016-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161128135703/http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2015/10/12/t-magazine/elizabeth-holmes-tech-visionaries-brian-chesky.html?_r=1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-12-10/can-theranos-ceo-elizabeth-holmes-fend-off-her-critics-|title=Can Elizabeth Holmes Save Her Unicorn?|work=Bloomberg Businessweek|author1=Kolhatkar, Sheelah|author2=Chen, Caroline|date=2015-12-10|access-date=2016-10-20|archive-date=2016-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160925074429/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-12-10/can-theranos-ceo-elizabeth-holmes-fend-off-her-critics-|dead-url=no}}</ref>。霍姆斯提到她的[[針頭恐懼症|針頭恐懼症]]是她成立Theranos的動力之一<ref name="auto"/><ref name="Bilton"/>。霍姆斯最早向她在史丹佛大學的幾位教授（其中包括Phyllis Gardner）提出「從指尖的幾滴血中搜集大量数据」時，大部份的人認為「幾乎不可能作到這點，不會有實質成效」，不過霍姆斯成功地讓工程學院院長錢寧·羅伯遜支持她的想法<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.vanityfair.com/news/2016/09/elizabeth-holmes-theranos-exclusive|title=How Elizabeth Holmes’s House of Cards Came Tumbling Down|first=Nick|last=Bilton|work=Vanity Fair|accessdate=2018-05-20|archive-date=2017-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170903233330/https://www.vanityfair.com/news/2016/09/elizabeth-holmes-theranos-exclusive|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

霍姆斯在2004年4月成立了公司，公司名稱是[[Theranos|Theranos]]，是therapy（治療）和diagnosis（診斷）的混成詞<ref name="msn.com">{{cite news|url=http://www.msn.com/en-us/money/smallbusiness/theranos%E2%80%99-elizabeth-holmes-young-entrepreneurs-need-%E2%80%9Ca-mission%E2%80%9D/ar-BBgje13|title=Theranos’ Elizabeth Holmes: Young entrepreneurs need "a mission"|work=MSN|accessdate=2015-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160428015228/http://www.msn.com/en-us/money/smallbusiness/theranos%E2%80%99-elizabeth-holmes-young-entrepreneurs-need-%E2%80%9Ca-mission%E2%80%9D/ar-BBgje13|archive-date=2016-04-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，並且租用了一個<!--group college house的-->地下室<ref name="newy_OneW"/>。霍姆斯也雇用了第一名員工，並且租用實驗室空間<ref name="online"/>。羅伯遜成為公司的第一位董事，並且向許多創業投資者介紹霍姆斯<ref name="newy_OneW"/>。

===獲得資金及擴張===
Theranos在其破產之前，曾經有一段驚人的成長。霍姆斯在2004年12月為Theranos找到了六百萬美元的投資資金<ref name="newy_OneW"/><ref name="online">{{Cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424127887324123004579055003869574012/|title=Elizabeth Holmes: The Breakthrough of Instant Diagnosis|accessdate=2013-09-16|work=The Wall Street Journal|first=Joseph|last=Rago|date=2013-09-08|archive-date=2017-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301115751/https://www.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424127887324123004579055003869574012|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2010年底時，Theranos獲得的創投資金已超過$9200萬美元<ref name="inc-oct-2015"/>，霍姆斯在2011年7月和前國務卿[[乔治·普拉特·舒尔茨|乔治·普拉特·舒尔茨]]見面，在二小時的會議後，舒尔茨加入霍姆斯的董事會<ref name="fortune2014">{{Cite web|url=http://fortune.com/2014/06/12/theranos-board-directors/|title=A singular board at Theranos|work=Fortune|author=Parloff, Roger|date=2014-06-12|access-date=2016-10-18|archive-date=2016-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161109082106/http://fortune.com/2014/06/12/theranos-board-directors/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，接下來的三年內，大家認為她「組織了美國企業史上最傑出的董事會」<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/sanfrancisco/print-edition/2013/08/02/theranos-adds-kovacevich-to-all-star.html|title=Theranos adds Kovacevich to all-star board|work=San Francisco Business Times|author=Leuty, Ron|date=2013-08-02|access-date=2016-10-18|archive-date=2017-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170414013237/http://www.bizjournals.com/sanfrancisco/print-edition/2013/08/02/theranos-adds-kovacevich-to-all-star.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。霍姆斯是用{{link-en|隱形模式|stealth mode}}經營此公司，沒有新聞，也沒有網站，一直到2013年9月，公司才宣佈和[[沃爾格林|沃爾格林]]合作，要建立在店內的血液樣品採集中心<ref name="economist-june-2016">{{Cite web|url=https://www.economist.com/news/business/21656193-theranoss-boss-says-her-mission-extends-beyond-making-fortune-holmes-where-heart|title=Holmes is where the heart is|work=The Economist|date=2015-06-27|access-date=2016-10-17|archive-date=2016-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161201221758/http://www.economist.com/news/business/21656193-theranoss-boss-says-her-mission-extends-beyond-making-fortune-holmes-where-heart|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/sanfrancisco/blog/biotech/2013/09/theranos-elizabeth-holmes-walgreens.html|title=Secretive Theranos emerging (partly) from shadows|work=San Francisco Business Times|author=Leuty, Ron|date=2013-09-09|access-date=2016-10-17|archive-date=2016-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160604162524/http://www.bizjournals.com/sanfrancisco/blog/biotech/2013/09/theranos-elizabeth-holmes-walgreens.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。霍姆斯在2014年登上《[[财富_(杂志)|财富]]》杂志、《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》杂志、《[[The_New_York_Times_Style_Magazine|T: The New York Times Style Magazine]]》杂志及《[[Inc.|Inc.]]》杂志，因此受到媒體的關注<ref name="recode-oct-2015">{{Cite web|url=http://www.recode.net/2015/10/26/11620036/theranos-ceo-elizabeth-holmess-five-best-cover-story-appearances|title=Theranos CEO Elizabeth Holmes's Five Best Cover Story Appearances, Ranked|publisher=Re/code|author=Kulwin, Noah|date=2015-10-26|access-date=2016-10-17|archive-date=2016-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018234632/http://www.recode.net/2015/10/26/11620036/theranos-ceo-elizabeth-holmess-five-best-cover-story-appearances|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》杂志認為霍姆斯是最年輕，自力致富的女性百萬富翁，在2014年的[[福布斯美国400富豪榜|福布斯美国400富豪榜]]中排名110名。Theranos評估值90億美元，而創投資金已超過$4億美元<ref name="newy_OneW"/><ref name=Forbes/>。在2014年底時，霍姆斯的名字出現在18個美國專利以及66個外國專利中<ref name="inc-july-2015"/>。2015年時，霍姆斯和[[克利夫兰诊所|克利夫兰诊所]]、Capital BlueCross及AmeriHealth Caritas簽署協議，允許他們使用Theranos的技術<ref name="inc-oct-2015"/>。

===Theranos的衰退===
《[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]》的John Carreyrou得到醫學專家透露的資訊，認為Theranos的血液檢測設備很可疑，因此開始了長達幾個月的秘密調查<ref name=badblood>{{cite book  |title=Bad Blood: Secrets and Lies in a Silicon Valley Startup |publisher=Knopf |author=John Carreyrou |year=2018 |page= |isbn=978-1524731656}}</ref>。Carreyrou和曾為Theranos員工的[[吹哨人|吹哨人]]，得到了郵件記錄等公司文件。霍姆斯在得知調查資訊後，透過她有力的律師{{link-en|David Boies|David Boies}}，透過法務及經濟手段，給《华尔街日报》及吹哨人壓力，試法讓John Carreyrou不要發表調查結果<ref name=badblood/>。儘管Boies有法律威脅和強硬手段，但John Carreyrou在2015年十月時發表了「重磅炸彈的報導」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/view/articles/2016-05-19/theranos-could-have-used-a-few-short-sellers |title=Theranos Could Have Used a Few Short Sellers |work=Bloomberg News |author=Justin Fox |date=2016-05-19 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |quote=John Carreyrou’s first bombshell article in the Wall Street Journal about problems at the blood-testing startup Theranos |archive-date=2018-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180815131429/https://www.bloomberg.com/view/articles/2016-05-19/theranos-could-have-used-a-few-short-sellers |dead-url=no }}</ref>，內容提到Theranos的[[血液检查|血液检查]]設備檢測的結果不準確，該公司使用市售的設備進行大部份的測試，以及其他足以定罪的資料<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/theranos-has-struggled-with-blood-tests-1444881901|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20151015043412/http://www.wsj.com/articles/theranos-has-struggled-with-blood-tests-1444881901#|archivedate=2015-10-15|deadurl=yes|title=Hot Startup Theranos Has Struggled With Its Blood-Test Technology|last=Carreyrou|first=John|date=2015-10-16|newspaper=Wall Street Journal|issn=0099-9660|access-date=2016-05-04}}</ref>。這是第一起媒體對Theranos的嚴厲批評，後續Carreyrou的一系列報導透露了更多更致命的細節。霍姆斯否認所有的指控，認為《华尔街日报》是「小報」，也表示會提供有關公司檢驗準確度的資料<ref>{{cite web|author=Stewart, James B.|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/30/business/the-narrative-frays-for-theranos-and-elizabeth-holmes.html|title=The Narrative Frays for Theranos and Elizabeth Holmes|date=2015-10-30|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2018-10-18|archive-date=2017-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170206184041/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/30/business/the-narrative-frays-for-theranos-and-elizabeth-holmes.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Pollack, Andrew|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/27/business/chief-of-theranos-pledges-to-prove-blood-tests-reliability.html|title=Theranos Chief Yields to Calls for Proof of Blood Test’s Reliability|date=2015-10-27|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2018-10-18|archive-date=2016-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160722113748/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/27/business/chief-of-theranos-pledges-to-prove-blood-tests-reliability.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。霍姆斯在報導見報的當天晚上上了Jim Cramer的《{{link-en|Mad Money|Mad Money}}》節目。Cramer提到說：「這篇報導非常殘酷。」，霍姆斯回應說「當你要作些改變時，就會出現這樣的事，一開始其他人認為你瘋了，接著和你對抗，接下來突然你就改變全世界了。」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2015/10/15/theranos-ceo-fires-back-at-wsj-i-was-shocked.html |title=Theranos CEO fires back at WSJ: I was shocked |work=Mad Money |author=Abigail Stevenson |date=2015-10-15 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |archive-date=2018-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180815200748/https://www.cnbc.com/2015/10/15/theranos-ceo-fires-back-at-wsj-i-was-shocked.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

{{link-en|美國醫保與醫助服務中心|Centers for Medicare and Medicaid Services}}（CMS）檢查了Theranos在加州[[紐華克_(加利福尼亞州)|紐華克]]的實驗室，發現其員工熟悉度、流程及設備均有不合規定之處，因此在2016年1月發出警告信給Theranos<ref>{{cite web|author=Duhaime-Ross, Arielle|url=https://www.theverge.com/2016/2/1/10869764/theranos-lab-warning-letter-consequences-patients|title=Here’s what Theranos customers need to know|date=2016-02-02|work=Verge|accessdate=2018-10-28|archive-date=2017-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171214182635/https://www.theverge.com/2016/2/1/10869764/theranos-lab-warning-letter-consequences-patients|dead-url=no}}</ref>。若Theranos在同年三月未能改善其加州實驗室的問題，CMS監管單位會在接下來的二年內禁止霍姆斯擁有或經營血液實驗室<ref>{{cite news|last1=Abelson|first1=Reed|title=Theranos Under Fire as U.S. Threatens Crippling Sanctions|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/04/14/business/theranos-elizabeth-holmes-proposed-ban.html|accessdate=2016-04-14|agency=The New York Times|date=2016-04-13|archive-date=2016-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414233345/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/04/14/business/theranos-elizabeth-holmes-proposed-ban.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。霍姆斯在NBC的《[[今天_(NBC)|今天]]》節目中提到<!--，'', Holmes said that she was "devastated we did not catch and fix these issues faster" and that--->會在新的科學及醫學諮詢委員會的幫助下重建實驗室<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.today.com/video/theranos-ceo-elizabeth-holmes-i-m-devastated-about-blood-test-issues-668286019825|title=Theranos CEO Elizabeth Holmes: I’m ‘devastated’ about blood test issues|publisher=The Today Show|date=2016-04-18|access-date=2016-10-18|archive-date=2016-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017101654/http://www.today.com/video/theranos-ceo-elizabeth-holmes-i-m-devastated-about-blood-test-issues-668286019825|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國醫保與醫助服務中心在2016年7月禁止霍姆斯在二年內擁有、經營或指導血液檢測服務（Theranos有向[[美国卫生及公共服务部|美国卫生及公共服务部]]提出申訴）<ref name = "Bilton"/><ref>Michael Siconolfi, John Carreyrou & Christopher Weaver, [https://www.wsj.com/articles/u-s-regulator-bans-theranos-ceo-elizabeth-holmes-from-operating-labs-for-two-years-1467956064 U.S. Regulator Bans Theranos CEO Elizabeth Holmes From Operating Labs for Two Years] {{Wayback|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/u-s-regulator-bans-theranos-ceo-elizabeth-holmes-from-operating-labs-for-two-years-1467956064 |date=20170309065920 }}, ''Wall Street Journal'' (July 8, 2016).</ref>。之後不久，[[沃爾格林|沃爾格林]]結束和Theranos的合作關係，也關閉其門市的血液收集中心。FDA也命令Theranos停用其毛細納米管裝置，這是Theranos的主要發明產品之一<ref name="FDA 2015-09-16">{{cite web |title=Pharmacy Inspection, Theranos, Inc., Newark, CA 483 |date=2015-09-16 |first=Ramesh |last=Balwani |accessdate=2018-05-18 |publisher=FDA |location=Washington, DC |url=https://www.fda.gov/ucm/groups/fdagov-public/@fdagov-afda-orgs/documents/document/ucm469395.pdf |archive-date=2018-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180414225004/https://www.fda.gov/ucm/groups/fdagov-public/@fdagov-afda-orgs/documents/document/ucm469395.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

亞利桑那州在2017年向Theranos提出訴訟，指控該公司賣了150萬血液測試產品給亞利桑那州居民，但是卻隱匿或歪曲有關測試產品的重要資訊。Theranos公司在同年4月答應將測試產品的費用退回給顧客，並且賠償美金$225,000的罰金及律師費，共計465萬美元<ref name=BISettlement>{{cite news|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/theranos-reaches-465-million-settlement-with-arizona-attorney-general-2017-4|title=Theranos just agreed to refund 175,000 people in Arizona who took its tests|last1=Ramsey|first1=Lydia|publisher=Business Insider|date=2017-04-18|access-date=2018-09-08|archive-date=2018-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181028225621/https://www.businessinsider.com/theranos-reaches-465-million-settlement-with-arizona-attorney-general-2017-4|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其他相關的事件包括[[美国证券交易委员会|美国证券交易委员会]]、{{link-en|加利福尼亞州北部地區檢察官辦公室|U.S. Attorney's Office for the Northern District of California}}及[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]針對民事及刑事的調查，以及二起[[詐騙|詐騙]]的[[集体诉讼|集体诉讼]]。霍姆斯<!--支持公司表示的看法，-->否認公司在過程中有不當之處<ref name = "Bilton"/>。

2017年5月16日，約99%的Theranos股東和公司和解，願意撤回所有当前和潜在的诉讼，換取[[優先股|優先股]]的股份。霍姆斯釋放了她部份的[[股東權益|股東權益]]，抵消對於未參與股東其股东价值的稀释<ref>{{Cite press release|url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20170516006652/en/Theranos-Finalizes-Shareholder-Recapitalization|title=Theranos Finalizes Shareholder Recapitalization|publisher=Theranos Inc.|date=2017-05-16|access-date=2018-10-28|archive-date=2017-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170825061647/http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20170516006652/en/Theranos-Finalizes-Shareholder-Recapitalization|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Balakrishnan|first1=Anita|title=Theranos' Elizabeth Holmes is giving away her shares to dodge lawsuits, report says|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2017/03/23/theranos-sell-shares-to-investors-promise-not-to-sue.html|accessdate=2017-04-10|agency=CNBC|date=2017-03-23|archive-date=2017-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170411055602/https://www.cnbc.com/2017/03/23/theranos-sell-shares-to-investors-promise-not-to-sue.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===刑事指控===
在[[旧金山|旧金山]]的美国检察官办公室二年的調查後，{{link-en|联邦大陪审团|federal grand jury}}指控霍姆斯以及Theranos前COO及总裁{{link-en|Ramesh Balwani|Ramesh Balwani}}涉及九项电匯欺詐以及二項串謀欺詐行為。檢查官認為霍姆斯和Balwani涉及二項犯罪計劃，一個是針對投資者的，另一個則是針對醫師及病患<ref name=":1"/><ref name="Carreyrou">Carreyrou, John (June 15, 2018). "[https://www.wsj.com/articles/u-s-files-criminal-charges-against-theranoss-elizabeth-holmes-ramesh-balwani-1529096005 U.S. Files Criminal Charges Against Theranos's Elizabeth Holmes, Ramesh Balwani] {{Wayback|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/u-s-files-criminal-charges-against-theranoss-elizabeth-holmes-ramesh-balwani-1529096005 |date=20180616003009 }}", ''Wall Street Journal''.</ref>。霍姆斯在起訴書發布後辭去了Theranos的CEO職務，不過仍為董事長<ref name="StepsDown"/>。

[[美国加利福尼亚北区联邦地区法院|美国加利福尼亚北区联邦地区法院]]對此案件進行審理，霍姆斯和Balwani表示沒有犯罪<ref>Mole, Beth (June 15, 2018). [https://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2018/06/disgraced-theranos-founder-elizabeth-holmes-indicted-on-criminal-charges/ "Disgraced Theranos founder Elizabeth Holmes indicted on criminal charges"] {{Wayback|url=https://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2018/06/disgraced-theranos-founder-elizabeth-holmes-indicted-on-criminal-charges/ |date=20210127071844 }}, ''Ars Technica''</ref>。2022年1月，陪審團裁定霍姆斯犯下包括刑事欺詐罪在內的4項罪名，不過欺詐病人的罪名不成立。<ref>{{cite news |title=Theranos創辦人、「女版喬布斯」Elizabeth Holmes欺詐投資者罪成 |url=https://finance.mingpao.com/fin/instantf/20220104/1641265627458/theranos%E5%89%B5%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%BA-%E3%80%8C%E5%A5%B3%E7%89%88%E5%96%AC%E5%B8%83%E6%96%AF%E3%80%8Delizabeth-holmes%E6%AC%BA%E8%A9%90%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90 |accessdate=2022-01-04 |archive-date=2022-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220104115558/https://finance.mingpao.com/fin/instantf/20220104/1641265627458/theranos%e5%89%b5%e8%be%a6%e4%ba%ba-%e3%80%8c%e5%a5%b3%e7%89%88%e5%96%ac%e5%b8%83%e6%96%af%e3%80%8delizabeth-holmes%e6%ac%ba%e8%a9%90%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87%e8%80%85%e7%bd%aa%e6%88%90 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

霍爾姆斯56歲前男友兼合夥人Sunny Balwani則被控12項欺詐罪。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e4%b8%96%e7%b4%80%e9%a8%99%e6%a1%88%ef%bd%9c%e4%b8%80%e6%bb%b4%e8%a1%80%e9%a9%97%e7%99%be%e7%97%85-%e5%a5%b3%e7%89%88%e5%96%ac%e5%b8%83%e6%96%af%e8%a9%90%e9%a8%99%e7%bd%aa%e6%88%90-299966 |title=世紀騙案｜一滴血驗百病 女版喬布斯詐騙罪成 |access-date=2022-01-05 |archive-date=2022-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220105001901/https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E4%B8%96%E7%B4%80%E9%A8%99%E6%A1%88%EF%BD%9C%E4%B8%80%E6%BB%B4%E8%A1%80%E9%A9%97%E7%99%BE%E7%97%85-%E5%A5%B3%E7%89%88%E5%96%AC%E5%B8%83%E6%96%AF%E8%A9%90%E9%A8%99%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-299966 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==行銷活動==
霍姆斯在2015年6月和墨西哥商人[[卡洛斯·斯利姆|卡洛斯·斯利姆]]合作，提昇[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]的血液檢查<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.forbes.com/sites/doliaestevez/2015/06/22/with-carlos-slim-billionaire-elizabeth-holmes-brings-innovative-blood-testing-method-to-mexico/#8a29eafa7892 | title = With Carlos Slim, Billionaire Elizabeth Holmes Brings Innovative Blood Testing Method To Mexico | work = Forbes | date = 2015-06-22 | accessdate = 2016-10-24 | author = Estevez, Dolia | archive-date = 2016-10-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161025114344/http://www.forbes.com/sites/doliaestevez/2015/06/22/with-carlos-slim-billionaire-elizabeth-holmes-brings-innovative-blood-testing-method-to-mexico/#8a29eafa7892 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。她在2015年10月宣佈#IronSisters，幫助女性從事科學、技術、工程及數學（[[STEM|STEM]]）的工作<ref>{{cite web | url = http://fortune.com/2015/10/12/elizabeth-holmes-calls-on-women/ | title = Theranos' Elizabeth Holmes calls on women to help each other | work = Fortune | date = 2015-10-12 | accessdate = 2016-10-24 | author = Lev-Ram, Michal | archive-date = 2016-10-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161025111431/http://fortune.com/2015/10/12/elizabeth-holmes-calls-on-women/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。她也幫助起草一項亞歷桑那州的法律，讓當地居民可以在沒有保險或醫療照顧提供者的批准下，獲得<!--and pay for-->實驗室的測試。不過這也誤導了大眾對Theranos準確性及有效性的認知，並且讓大眾成為不知情的受實驗者<ref name=badblood/><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/2015/07/02/new-arizona-law-and-fda-approval-gives-theranos-something-to-celebrate/29634373/ | title = Now no doctor’s note needed for blood test in Arizona | work = USA Today | date = 2015-07-02 | accessdate = 2016-10-24 | author = della Cava, Marco | archive-date = 2016-12-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161201075629/http://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/2015/07/02/new-arizona-law-and-fda-approval-gives-theranos-something-to-celebrate/29634373/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==人脈==
霍姆斯認識許多具有影響力，而且支持她的人<ref name=badblood/>。董事會的十二名成員中包括前國務卿[[亨利·基辛格|亨利·基辛格]]、前國防部長[[威廉·佩里|威廉·佩里]]、前國務卿[[乔治·普拉特·舒尔茨|乔治·普拉特·舒尔茨]]、前參議員{{link-en|山姆·纳恩|Sam Nunn}}及[[比爾·弗利斯特|比爾·弗利斯特]]、前海軍上將{{link-en|蓋里·羅海德|Gary Roughea}}、前國防部長[[詹姆斯·马蒂斯|詹姆斯·马蒂斯]]、以及富國銀行的前CEO {{link-en|Dick Kovacevich|Dick Kovacevich}}及比奇特尔公司的前CEO {{link-en|Riley Bechtel|Riley Bechtel}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://fortune.com/2015/10/15/theranos-board-leadership/ |title=Theranos' board: Plenty of political connections, little relevant expertise |work=Fortune |author=Jennifer Reingold |date=2015-10-15 |accessdate=2018-09-06 |archive-date=2018-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180906195744/http://fortune.com/2015/10/15/theranos-board-leadership/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她高調的私人投資者包括媒体大亨[[鲁伯特·默多克|鲁伯特·默多克]]、川普總統任內的教育部長[[贝琪·德沃斯|贝琪·德沃斯]]、沃尔玛的沃尔顿家族、{{link-en|考克斯企业|Cox Enterprises}}的考克斯家族以及墨西哥百萬富翁卡洛斯斯利姆，在公司倒閉時都損失了上百萬美金<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/05/04/health/theranos-investors-murdoch-devos-walmart.html |title=Caught in the Theranos Wreckage: Betsy DeVos, Rupert Murdoch and Walmart’s Waltons |work=NY Times |author=Reed Abelson |date=2018-05-04 |accessdate=2018-09-06 |archive-date=2018-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180906233715/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/05/04/health/theranos-investors-murdoch-devos-walmart.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。霍姆斯是[[希拉里·克林顿|希拉里·克林顿]]2016年參選總統時的支持者之一，也是她女兒[[切尔西·克林顿|切尔西·克林顿]]的朋友<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2016/3/22/11285476/here-s-a-picture-of-theranos-ceo-elizabeth-holmes-and-chelsea-clinton|title=Here’s a picture of Theranos CEO Elizabeth Holmes and Chelsea Clinton|publisher=|access-date=2019-01-04|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115081431/https://www.theverge.com/2016/3/22/11285476/here-s-a-picture-of-theranos-ceo-elizabeth-holmes-and-chelsea-clinton|dead-url=no}}</ref>。曾在 2015 年擔任過時任美國總統歐巴馬的「全球創業大使」（Presidential Ambassadors for Global Entrepreneurship, PAGE）之一<ref>{{Cite web|title=Elizabeth Holmes quietly stepped down from Obama’s business ambassador program|url=https://social.techcrunch.com/2016/08/02/elizabeth-holmes-quietly-stepped-down-from-obamas-business-ambassador-program/|access-date=2022-01-06|work=TechCrunch|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=「矽谷世紀大騙局」為何能一路瞞天過海？從《惡血》看政商名流、媒體與監管機構的失職｜台客 J／台客 J 的橘色筆記｜換日線|url=https://crossing.cw.com.tw/article/13999|access-date=2022-01-06|work=換日線 Crossing|language=zh-TW}}</ref>。2015年時任副總統拜登參觀Theranos公司。[https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/10/08/0/14214267.jpg&x=0&y=0&sw=0&sh=0&sl=W&fw=1050] {{Wayback|url=https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F10%2F08%2F0%2F14214267.jpg&x=0&y=0&sw=0&sh=0&sl=W&fw=1050 |date=20211202173219 }}<ref>{{Cite web|title=Theranos詐欺大審判：「惡血」之女的反英雄之辯？|url=https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8664/5803254|access-date=2022-01-06|last=聯合新聞網|work=轉角國際 udn Global|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2022-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220106211640/https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8664/5803254|dead-url=no}}</ref>

霍姆斯也有私人的友誼，她常以友人的身份參加[[乔治·普拉特·舒尔茨|乔治·普拉特·舒尔茨]]的家庭派對。舒尔茨的孫子泰勒·舒尔茨才大學畢業，就在Theranos開始了第一份工作。他也是向華爾街日報的John Carreyrou透露公司腐败问题的举报人之一。得知此事後，霍姆斯透過律師David Boies威脅，若泰勒繼續透露消息，她要告舒尔茨家庭，並且使其破產<ref name=badblood/>。乔治·普拉特·舒尔茨忠於霍姆斯，要孫子泰勒不要再透露消息給《華爾街日報》<ref name=badblood/>。

==獎項==
在Theranos解體之前，霍姆斯受到廣泛的好評。她曾被評為《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》2015年最具影響力人物之一<ref name="time-april-2015"/>，獲得《福布斯》雜誌的Under 30 Doers奬項，名列在2015年的「最有權力女性」名單中<ref name="Forbes-Under30award">{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/sarahhedgecock/2015/10/05/elizabeth-holmes-on-using-business-to-change-the-world/#476cd48d202f|title=Elizabeth Holmes On Using Business To Change The World|last1=Hedgecock|first1=Sarah|website=Forbes|accessdate=2018-12-27|archive-date=2017-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170505182814/https://www.forbes.com/sites/sarahhedgecock/2015/10/05/elizabeth-holmes-on-using-business-to-change-the-world/#476cd48d202f|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/pictures/gjlk45ei/elizabeth-holmes/|title=The World's Most Powerful Women 2015: 19 Newcomers|date=2015|publisher=Forbes|accessdate=2016-06-11|archive-date=2016-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160612083451/http://www.forbes.com/pictures/gjlk45ei/elizabeth-holmes/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也被{{link-en|Glamour|Glamour (magazine)}}雜誌評為年度女性<ref name="Glamour-WOY">{{cite web|author=Fenn, Donna|url=http://www.glamour.com/story/elizabeth-holmes|title=Elizabeth Holmes Wants You to Have Control of Your Health Info|date=2015-10-29|website=Glamour Magazine|accessdate=2016-05-31|archive-date=2016-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160613032500/http://www.glamour.com/story/elizabeth-holmes|dead-url=no}}</ref>。霍姆斯獲得2015年的{{link-en|Horatio Alger獎|Horatio Alger Association of Distinguished Americans}}，是該獎項最年輕的得獎者<ref name="Fortune-Horatio-award">{{cite web|url=http://fortune.com/2014/12/03/theranos-elizabeth-holmes-young-fortune-mpw-next-gen/|title=Theranos' Elizabeth Holmes: Young entrepreneurs need "a mission"|last1=Parloff|first1=Roger|website=Fortune|accessdate=2016-05-31|archive-date=2016-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160703024947/http://fortune.com/2014/12/03/theranos-elizabeth-holmes-young-fortune-mpw-next-gen/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Horatio2">{{cite web|url=https://www.horatioalger.org/members/member-detail/?id=003j000000ibsbJAAQ|title=2015 Horatio Alger Award Winner Elizabeth Holmes|website=Horatio Alger Association of Distinguished Americans|accessdate=2016-05-31|archive-date=2016-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160807121007/https://www.horatioalger.org/members/member-detail/?id=003j000000ibsbJAAQ|dead-url=no}}</ref>。霍姆斯也曾獲得《財富》雜誌的年度最佳商業人士，並年列40 Under 40名單中<ref>{{cite web|url=http://fortune.com/businessperson-of-the-year/2014/elizabeth-holmes-14/?iid=leftrail|title=14. Elizabeth Holmes|date=2014|publisher=Fortune|accessdate=2016-06-11|archive-date=2016-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160910105144/http://fortune.com/businessperson-of-the-year/2014/elizabeth-holmes-14/?iid=leftrail|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://fortune.com/40-under-40/2014/elizabeth-holmes-9/|title=9. Elizabeth Holmes|date=2014|publisher=Fortune|accessdate=2016-06-11|archive-date=2016-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611102109/http://fortune.com/40-under-40/2014/elizabeth-holmes-9/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

後來Theranos的許多新聞曝光，也有多筆有關Theranos的刑事訴訟及民事訴訟，[[美国证券交易委员会|美国证券交易委员会]]指控霍姆斯是大規模欺詐<ref name="auto1">{{Cite news|author=della Cava, Marco|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/2018/03/14/theranos-founder-elizabeth-holmes-charged-massive-fraud/424670002/|title=She was 'the next Steve Jobs.' Now, Theranos founder Elizabeth Holmes is charged with fraud|work=USA Today|access-date=2018-03-16|language=en|archive-date=2018-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180315140702/https://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/2018/03/14/theranos-founder-elizabeth-holmes-charged-massive-fraud/424670002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《財富》在2016年將霍姆斯列為「全世界最令人失望的領導者」之一<ref name="Fortune">{{Cite web|url=http://fortune.com/2016/03/30/most-disappointing-leaders/|title=The World's 19 Most Disappointing Leaders|date=2016-03-30|work=Fortune|access-date=2016-12-02|archive-date=2016-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161123145216/http://fortune.com/2016/03/30/most-disappointing-leaders/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==個人生活==
[[File:Nuclear_nonproliferation_discussion_130417-D-NI589-107_cropped.jpg|thumb]]
在2018年Theranos解散之前，伊莉莎白·霍姆斯有Theranos 50%的股份<ref name="Roger2014"/>，《福布斯》將她列為美國最有錢、白手起家的女性之一，資產45億美元<ref name="Forbes">{{Cite web|title = Elizabeth Holmes|url = https://www.forbes.com/profile/elizabeth-holmes/|website = Forbes|accessdate = 2015-12-09|archive-date = 2014-10-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141021025944/http://www.forbes.com/profile/elizabeth-holmes/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。《福布斯》在2016年6月更新Theranos的價值8億美元，這使得霍姆斯的股份變的沒有價值，因為其他持有特別股的投資者可以在霍姆斯（只持有普通股）之前優先獲得清債<ref name="Forbes_nothing">{{Cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/matthewherper/2016/06/01/from-4-5-billion-to-nothing-forbes-revises-estimated-net-worth-of-theranos-founder-elizabeth-holmes|title=From $4.5 Billion To Nothing: Forbes Revises Estimated Net Worth Of Theranos Founder Elizabeth Holmes|last=Herper|first=Matthew|date=2016-06-01|work=Forbes|access-date=2017-01-06|archive-date=2019-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216095750/https://www.forbes.com/sites/matthewherper/2016/06/01/from-4-5-billion-to-nothing-forbes-revises-estimated-net-worth-of-theranos-founder-elizabeth-holmes/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據報導，霍姆斯因為行使選擇權，欠Theranos 2500萬美元的債務。她沒有從其中收到現金，也沒有賣掉她那些有關債務的股票<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/theranos-founder-elizabeth-holmes-owes-about-25-million-to-blood-testing-startup-1491435009|title=Theranos Founder Elizabeth Holmes Owes About $25 Million to Blood-Testing Startup|first=Christopher|last=Weaver|date=2017-04-05|work=Wall Street Journal|accessdate=2018-01-25|archive-date=2018-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180125134826/https://www.wsj.com/articles/theranos-founder-elizabeth-holmes-owes-about-25-million-to-blood-testing-startup-1491435009|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Shen|first1=Lucinda|title=Theranos Founder Elizabeth Holmes Reportedly Owes Her Startup $25 Million|url=http://fortune.com/2017/04/06/theranos-founder-elizabeth-holmes-reportedly-25-million/|accessdate=2017-04-10|work=Fortune|date=2017-04-06|archive-date=2017-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170409142935/http://fortune.com/2017/04/06/theranos-founder-elizabeth-holmes-reportedly-25-million/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Balakrishnan|first1=Anita|title=Founder Elizabeth Holmes reportedly owes Theranos about $25 million|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2017/04/05/founder-elizabeth-holmes-reportedly-owes-theranos-about-25-million.html|accessdate=2017-04-10|work=CNBC|date=2017-04-05|archive-date=2017-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170409022349/https://www.cnbc.com/2017/04/05/founder-elizabeth-holmes-reportedly-owes-theranos-about-25-million.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

